    <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;background:white;">
        <b><span style="color:#000000;">2. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; QUYỀN RIÊNG TƯ</span></b> 
